  Locus:
    Page: 36
    Verse: 20
Tags:
  - The body has one fault
---
Don’t pay too much attention to thebody. If you worry about the well-
beingof your body, you identify with it moreand more. Look upon it as a
usefulvehicle： maintain it, fuel it properlyand repair it if it breaks
down, butdon’t become attached to it.
